Class.name: cAdmin.data.Database
Class.Description: This class contins all information about database

Property.name: Path
Property.Description: String, contaiinig path to the database

Property.name: DirectorySpace
Property.Description: Availible free space for the database

Property.name: DBWrites
Property.Description: Writes per minute to the listed mounted database

Property.name: DBReads
Property.Description: Reads per minute from the listed mounted database

Property.name: DBLatency
Property.Description: Milliseconds to complete a random read from the listed mounted database
